Title: Check_MK service: Piggyback data source reports the source hosts now
Level: 1
Component: core
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0b1
Date: 1532636234

The Check_MK service now reports the source hosts that provided piggyback
information for the processed host. This makes debugging a lot easier when
working with piggyback information.
